lead_paragraph: FATAL ACCIDENT--THREE PERSONS DROWNED.--Last Sunday afternoon Robert T. Seymour, Esq., Coroner, was called to hold an inquest on the body of a woman named Cragin, who, together with another woman named O'Hara, and a man, were drowned in the river near the Slate Dock.
